        closedBy: null,
        body: '## Description  \r\nFluent dark and bootstrap dark themes appear to have some white borders leftover in them when applied to the `igx-grid`.\r\n\r\n * igniteui-angular version: 10.0.5\r\n * browser: Chrome\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce  \r\n\r\n1. Open this grid sample https://www.infragistics.com/products/ignite-ui-angular/angular/components/grid/editing.html\r\n2. Change the theme to fluent dark or bootstrap dark\r\n\r\n## Result  \r\nPaging border and scrollbar borders are white.\r\n\r\n## Expected result  \r\nThe borders should be consistent with the theme.\r\n\r\n## Attachments  \r\n![image_2020_07_21T07_24_25_975Z](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1472513/88031479-51932080-cb45-11ea-94a8-a145ebd55e15.png)\r\n![image_2020_07_21T07_23_07_279Z](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1472513/88031482-53f57a80-cb45-11ea-9f90-911745f2d098.png)\r\n\r\n',
