        body: '## Description  \r\nNot sure why a Watermark is displayed in the most recent version of igniteui-angular 9.1.0? \r\n Watermark "Trial version of IgniteUI for Angular" displays inside bottom right corner of IgxGridComponent.  The word "trial" displays inside background of IgxGridComponent\r\n\r\n * igniteui-angular version: 9.1.0\r\n * browser: Version 83.0.4103.61 (Official Build) (64-bit)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce  \r\n\r\n1. Open View that contains IgxGridComponent\r\n2. Watermark displays inside bottom right corner of IgxGridComponent\r\n3. The word "trial" displays inside background image of IgxGridComponent\r\n\r\n## Result  \r\nWhat is the actual result after following the steps to reproduce?\r\nWatermark **"Trial version of IgniteUI for Angular"** displays inside bottom right corner of IgxGridComponent.  The word "trial" displays inside background of IgxGridComponent\r\n\r\n## Expected result  \r\nWhat is the expected result after following the steps to reproduce?\r\nWatermark should not display inside IgxGridComponent. The word "trial" should not display inside background of IgxGridComponent.\r\n\r\n## Attachments  \r\nAttach a sample if available, and screenshots, if applicable.  \r\n\r\n',
